# Decentralized-AI-project
I would like to build a decentralized AI project - decentralized inference (distributing token generation across nodes).
It will be aimed for very small models. I just think it is cool and I would like to learn how it works more deeply and think about this problem - and what better way than trying out some simplified version on my own.

(better README will be added after further functionality)
